feat(fax): cleaner preview, prev/next nav, prefetch & hide order items

PDF preview cleanup:
- Add #toolbar=0&navpanes=0&scrollbar=0&view=FitH to iframe URL,
  hides Chrome's PDF reader sidebar and toolbar that confused users
- Lighter background (#E8E8E8) for better readability

Detail navigation:
- Add 上一個 / 下一個 buttons with current/total indicator
- Keyboard shortcuts: ArrowLeft / ArrowRight / Escape
- Ordering follows the current INBOX filter

Preview loading optimization:
- Cache signed URLs in a ref Map (valid 1h, survives navigation)
- Prefetch adjacent faxes' signed URLs in background → instant nav
- Loading overlay is now semi-transparent so previous content stays
  visible during transition (no more blank flash)
- Stop falling back to broken public URLs (bucket is private)

Order items hidden:
- Replace order items table with a single hint line ("含 N 筆品項")
  since AI extraction is unreliable for handwritten/scanned faxes;
  users should rely on the actual preview instead
- special_notes still shown — that's the field operators care about
